sequenceDiagram
    participant BM as BenchmarkRunner
    participant DFA as DeterministicFixtureAgent
    participant DRA as OpenCodeDryRunAgent
    participant EC as EvidenceContract
    participant FS as FileSystem (.positron/evidence/)

    BM->>BM: Check executionMode

    alt fixture mode
        BM->>DFA: execute(scenario, input)
        DFA->>DFA: Look up fixture in Map
        DFA-->>BM: EvidenceReport (status, simulatedActions)
        BM->>EC: determineConclusionStatus(issues)
        BM->>FS: Write run-summary.fixture.json
    else dry-run mode
        BM->>DRA: analyzeActions(plannedActions, input)
        DRA->>DRA: Check kill switches
        DRA->>DRA: classifyOperation() per action
        DRA-->>BM: EvidenceReport (simulated, blocked, reported)
        BM->>EC: Build BenchmarkIssueResult per issue
        BM->>FS: Write run-summary.dry-run.json
    end

    BM->>BM: Build conclusion (GREEN/YELLOW/RED/UNKNOWN)
    BM->>BM: Build capabilityDelta
    BM-->>Caller: RudolphBenchmarkRunSummary
